        "subject": "LU-5781 osc: check for extents under lock for lru cancel",
        "message": "LU-5781 osc: check for extents under lock for lru cancel\n\nosc_lock_weight() should try to cancel PW locks as well, however\nchecking for pages in gang_lookup as was done in LU-3321 wasted\nmost of the time for looking through cached unused pages.\n\nreplace it by a check for osc_extents, which covers regions of\npages and exists only till the IO completion.\n\nSigned-off-by: Vitaly Fertman <vitaly_fertman@xyratex.com>\nChange-Id: Id3f93ac0b1e3643269b32376c75e1f3a67715430\nSeagate-bug-id: MRP-2176\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
